Retreatment for prostate cancer with stereotactic body radiation therapy (SBRT): 
Feasible or foolhardy?

Arcangeli S(1), Agolli L(2), Donato V(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Radiotherapy, Azienda Ospedaliera S. Camillo-Forlanini, Rome, 
Italy.
