Author information:
(1)Department of Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery (Head: Prof. Dr. Max Heiland), 
University Medical Center Hamburg Eppendorf, Martinistraße 52, 20246 Hamburg, 
Germany. Electronic address: c.rendenbach@uke.de.
(2)Department of Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery (Head: Prof. Dr. Max Heiland), 
